note-structure:
a
owl:Ontology
dct:contributor
Roberta Padlina, project coordinator and software developer, Basel University, Switzerland
and
Reto Baumgartner, tool coordinator and software developer, University of Zürich, Switzerland (en)
dct:creator
Hans Cools, MD, knowledge engineer, ontologist, software developer, Basel University, Switzerland
dct:description
Formal description of note structure, subclasses, related classes, and properties.
skos:note
Extension of the text structure ontology.
dct:publisher
Universities of Basel, Bern, and Zürich, Switzerland
dct:title
An ontology about note structure
owl:versionInfo
2020-06-11
